issue.title: Vector tile layers not visible on the Cesium map
issue.body:
Hi, I'm creating VectorTileLayers which display on the OL map but when switching to the Cesium one they disappear. I also have WKT layers that display correctly.
With some debugging I see that this line https://github.com/openlayers/ol-cesium/blob/v2.16/src/olcs/AbstractSynchronizer.ts#L116, is executed correctly for all layers including the VT ones, they just don't appear. 

Any suggestion?

Thanks in advance
